<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.10">
<l>allik kamalak kaṇṇaṉai yaṅkorāycci</l>
<l>yellip poḻutū ṭiyavū ṭaltiṟattai</l>
<l>kalliṉ malitōḷ kaliyaṉ coṉṉamālai</l>
<l>collit tutippā ravartuk kamilarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who praise him with eyes [like] the night[-blooming] lotus,</l>
<l>Reciting this garland [of verse] composed by Kaliyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">with arms as large as boulders,</l>
<l>About the sulkiness which a herdess felt there</l>
<l>In the nighttime, they will have no sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
